{"tid":516314,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[攝台] 2017我的攝影回顧","createTime":"2018-01-01T09:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T01:28:29.000Z","uid":14919,"like":29,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c6db9044002a0f4c15556808ee7e73e37ae62266","tid":516314,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4642/39423852571_78ff48f9f7_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4642%2F39423852571_78ff48f9f7_b.jpg&h=976ad93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影左菲林3年，發覺自己宜家影嘅相同一開始果陣差好遠，唔知其他人睇返自己以前影嘅相果陣，會唔會有一種「我以前究竟影緊咩」嘅感覺。<br />\n就算係睇返2017嘅相都好，都發覺年初影嘅相同年尾有唔少分別。所以，我就想整理下今年自己影嘅相，順便係度share埋，俾攝台嘅人評下，請多多指教。<br />\n<br />\n（d相大部分都係順次序影嘅，由年頭到年尾，所以應該睇得出我影相嘅心態有d唔同）<br />\n<br />\n我主要都係用35/50mm定焦影相<br />\n年頭大部分都係50mm，不過慢慢就轉多左35mm，感覺上可以容納到更多後面背景<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解 年初有一排好鍾意影俯瞰嘅相 <br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4729/24557862927_c55f08373c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4729%2F24557862927_c55f08373c_b.jpg&h=5270b1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#2<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4641/24557863257_0ff0d8a42a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4641%2F24557863257_0ff0d8a42a_b.jpg&h=66819868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#3<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4635/38545798915_b48d55c479_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4635%2F38545798915_b48d55c479_b.jpg&h=e5ef1fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係航拍機果種，而係由高少少嘅地方影<br />\n<br />\n#4<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4646/39393971012_20be58be2d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4646%2F39393971012_20be58be2d_b.jpg&h=a57e43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#5<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4637/25554023938_f21086c7ba_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4637%2F25554023938_f21086c7ba_b.jpg&h=1fe74ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如係天橋影落去咁<br />\n<br />\n#6<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4688/24557864447_9a09dd10ba_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4688%2F24557864447_9a09dd10ba_b.jpg&h=eaff3ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一年，尤其係年頭，我都影唔少深水埗或者d街市/舊墟嘅相<br />\n<br />\n#7<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4689/38716270604_6f099beeb3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4689%2F38716270604_6f099beeb3_b.jpg&h=0b624080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4730/25554022868_916cc49417_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4730%2F25554022868_916cc49417_b.jpg&h=97350720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#9<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4732/39423846781_7a605ee20c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4732%2F39423846781_7a605ee20c_b.jpg&h=22ae4ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種相好似幾受歡迎（起碼係ig係）<br />\n<br />\n#10<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4725/25554023318_bc9c869666_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4725%2F25554023318_bc9c869666_b.jpg&h=f42bfa36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年試過好多次由石硤尾行去深水埗，因為我覺得街拍黎講，咁行會經過好多有香港特色嘅地方<br />\n然後四月影左一張今年我ig最多like+cm嘅相<br />\n<br />\n#11<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4738/25554023048_3d42f81f86_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4738%2F25554023048_3d42f81f86_b.jpg&h=ec6e9b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後五月尾 我去左北歐（芬蘭+挪威），影左好多風景相<br />\n不過之前係度po過，d相唔再po啦，有興趣嘅就去果個睇下啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/270730/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/270730/</a><br />\n<br />\n係暑假果陣，我突然留意到，我嘅相好似無咩故事性<br />\n好多都係一個景+人咁<br />\n好似下面果d咁<br />\n<br />\n#12<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4681/27647076449_a1c8dd006b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4681%2F27647076449_a1c8dd006b_b.jpg&h=2044f9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#13<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4689/27647074609_b06dc66b86_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4689%2F27647074609_b06dc66b86_b.jpg&h=7623d979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#14<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4598/25554024578_224df40ed2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4598%2F25554024578_224df40ed2_b.jpg&h=a0c18a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#15<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4734/38716275054_86a92020b5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4734%2F38716275054_86a92020b5_b.jpg&h=91e8cf5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我就開始相係d相到多少少故事，唔係淨係以景為主<br />\n<br />\n#16<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4735/27647074109_654264e3c1_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4735%2F27647074109_654264e3c1_b.jpg&h=004ff010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#17<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4647/25554025498_e2e0d4a992_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4647%2F25554025498_e2e0d4a992_b.jpg&h=6c4a9964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#18<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4639/25554024898_2993a8fc94_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4639%2F25554024898_2993a8fc94_b.jpg&h=68f8ae7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#19<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4646/38545799735_9c0636fd08_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4646%2F38545799735_9c0636fd08_b.jpg&h=92132ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後今年有幾張相真係最滿意，尤其係下面果兩種<br />\n<br />\n#20<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4591/38545794355_a32ef32ff6_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4591%2F38545794355_a32ef32ff6_b.jpg&h=fc699a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#21<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4725/27647073299_08956f3305_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4725%2F27647073299_08956f3305_b.jpg&h=cbd68ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得上面兩張絕對係我嘅top 5<br />\n<br />\n講開又講，除左上面張相，我好少會係度等d人埋位<br />\n好多都係一剎那間<br />\n<br />\n然後今年七月去過一轉坪洲，無咩特別影到好特別嘅相<br />\n<br />\n#21<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4643/38545797415_2da8c54266_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4643%2F38545797415_2da8c54266_b.jpg&h=5d50713a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#22<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4594/38545796855_c362ff603d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4594%2F38545796855_c362ff603d_b.jpg&h=8875f9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#23<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4683/27647079119_815da2131d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4683%2F27647079119_815da2131d_b.jpg&h=1e20259c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我開始嘗試用多少少光同影<br />\n<br />\n#24<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4588/38545796035_a6319f721c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4588%2F38545796035_a6319f721c_b.jpg&h=75b48e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93d90c3047ccd3b1cd10f2a21c7e948f4ded533","tid":516314,"uid":14919,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"之後我都多左嘗試，無論係影人，定係街+景<br />\n以前就好似咁<br />\n<br />\n#25<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4643/38545798225_6ac02e59c9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4643%2F38545798225_6ac02e59c9_b.jpg&h=84c56563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前只要個人啱位就影，不過宜家多左用光影黎做對比<br />\n<br />\n#26<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4735/24557875307_d95de60834_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4735%2F24557875307_d95de60834_b.jpg&h=a5456a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#27<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4736/24557874997_fe2ffc73fa_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4736%2F24557874997_fe2ffc73fa_b.jpg&h=8f823768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#28<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4690/38545801295_dd23ee63f7_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4690%2F38545801295_dd23ee63f7_b.jpg&h=46c509e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#29<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4597/38545800725_6a20ff3378_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4597%2F38545800725_6a20ff3378_b.jpg&h=083ec117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#30<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4643/24557874477_409bc5ea2a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4643%2F24557874477_409bc5ea2a_b.jpg&h=a4a12282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#31<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4635/39423846251_fbde07963d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4635%2F39423846251_fbde07963d_b.jpg&h=55e7b92d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然有d顧及唔到光影，不過就會多少少故事<br />\n<br />\n#32<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4597/39423845641_c581e8427a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4597%2F39423845641_c581e8427a_b.jpg&h=3b615121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#33<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4599/38545802955_77fa147b84_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4599%2F38545802955_77fa147b84_b.jpg&h=aca5ff44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#34<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4590/38545799345_961617ea0b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4590%2F38545799345_961617ea0b_b.jpg&h=ca26a82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#35<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4683/27647083189_2e70158e53_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4683%2F27647083189_2e70158e53_b.jpg&h=27775999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，烏溪沙係另一個練習攝影嘅好地方<br />\n風景以外，影人都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n#36<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4641/39423848791_f63c6a817b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4641%2F39423848791_f63c6a817b_b.jpg&h=2237a884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#37<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4739/39423848211_def059f16a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4739%2F39423848211_def059f16a_b.jpg&h=d5619ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#38<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4683/39423847911_c4ef8c149c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4683%2F39423847911_c4ef8c149c_b.jpg&h=9726cf68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#39<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4731/38545807015_294500dd11_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4731%2F38545807015_294500dd11_b.jpg&h=de8893a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到大約十一月，我就開始用多左35mm做街拍<br />\n因為我好多時都係盲拍，所以轉用35mm方便左好多<br />\n不過影街道果d，都係鍾意50mm嘅透視感<br />\n<br />\n#40<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4644/25554040538_c9c88f8846_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4644%2F25554040538_c9c88f8846_b.jpg&h=d62534ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#41<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4693/39423850331_cc329e2fa5_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4693%2F39423850331_cc329e2fa5_b.jpg&h=3ac77b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#42<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4589/38545809945_0e20c7a9c9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4589%2F38545809945_0e20c7a9c9_b.jpg&h=816fa621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我越來越鍾意係d相到有一個對比嘅人，去襯托個主題<br />\n而唔係淨係得一個人，好似影人有一出一入咁<br />\n上面都有唔少係咁嘅概念<br />\n<br />\n#43<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4598/39423852951_28b6ba0e4d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4598%2F39423852951_28b6ba0e4d_b.jpg&h=38ee36b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#44<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4689/25554041268_2514965601_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4689%2F25554041268_2514965601_b.jpg&h=4837fd32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#45<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4682/39423851241_c73dfd5664_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4682%2F39423851241_c73dfd5664_b.jpg&h=eb2768e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面果張，我影果陣完全唔知佢望緊鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n#46<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4638/39423849101_f4f9f021e3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4638%2F39423849101_f4f9f021e3_b.jpg&h=ba6a7313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一兩張最近影嘅<br />\n<br />\n#47<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4683/39423852051_81c986df18_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4683%2F39423852051_81c986df18_b.jpg&h=705fd2a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#48<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4642/39423852571_78ff48f9f7_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4642%2F39423852571_78ff48f9f7_b.jpg&h=976ad93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我宜家多左出去行，不過快門明顯㩒少左，覺得好多畫面都唔夠好咁<br />\n由以前一半出去一個下午一定影到一筒，到宜家基本上可能得半筒<br />\n唔知咁樣係唔係一件好事，不過滿意嘅作品相對多左<br />\n<br />\n如果你地有d咩意見，就多d留言。<br />\n<br />\n最後留埋自己個ig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thomasthtc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthomasthtc%2F&d=tB0cEPxZ%2Bnlxh6ObiX%2BD4%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bfa036cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/thomasthtc/</a>"},{"pid":"c5db24ce355262d6c5a3d743ded65c75560f9dfb","tid":516314,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"cc9d49f9d994063bf2537ed1b8ca576ad98c9da3","tid":516314,"uid":42624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"個人幾鍾意20同21<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n22左邊可以再crop多d就正"},{"pid":"c21e85980b4f54a223bbc41cc860bf02bf573559","tid":516314,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"多留意構圖，按快門的時刻"},{"pid":"5d3eb159376c88ef673c559357281096cd87266a","tid":516314,"uid":76020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"有張同你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/185220_a5a9455a1dd2495107993b6ff09f297e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F185220_a5a9455a1dd2495107993b6ff09f297e.jpeg&h=f3f97d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74e5c9f8901a4ec6764c36cac484d711d0f3e295","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"原來係你<br />\n<br />\n巴打留意左你好耐"},{"pid":"6d53258931cd257a97c13d6ca0c9cbb9361b2af6","tid":516314,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e5c9f8901a4ec6764c36cac484d711d0f3e295","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"原來係你<br />\n<br />\n巴打留意左你好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"哦我識佢呀佢講野。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n番名跟大隊"},{"pid":"956bfead242eaeea2f2f727bdb6b42a5e3e77810","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宜家多左出去行，不過快門明顯㩒少左，覺得好多畫面都唔夠好咁<br />\n由以前一半出去一個下午一定影到一筒，到宜家基本上可能得半筒<br />\n唔知咁樣係唔係一件好事，不過滿意嘅作品相對多左<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凈係呢幾句野，其實我都唔知邊樣先啱。<br />\n<br />\n同你剛好倒轉，之前勁慳快門用勁多時間構圖諗清楚先㩒，錯失左好多機會，風景的話又真係輛率高好多，不過ｓｎａｐ　成日覺得背景亂構圖唔靚就唔影，ｍｉｓｓ　好多野喇<br />\n<br />\n而家風景ｓｎａｐｓｈｏｔ要兩個ｍｏｄｅ都仲適應緊"},{"pid":"42e9a818eb724d382dea1b581096121e6fefb885","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d53258931cd257a97c13d6ca0c9cbb9361b2af6","tid":516314,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e5c9f8901a4ec6764c36cac484d711d0f3e295","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"原來係你<br />\n<br />\n巴打留意左你好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"哦我識佢呀佢講野。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n番名跟大隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babc5db671d087ce96e3358ce3c82f6c918b137e","tid":516314,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"好似12，18，25嗰啲我都好鐘意<br />\n<br />\n但係放係攝台都會被人留低負皮同膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207ed514b68d1a2387a53009e8bac257a6c73f68","tid":516314,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:20:08.000Z","msg":"Good post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人係度開post放相<br />\n但好小人會講返自已當刻的感受<br />\n十分認同你的做法<br />\n<br />\n街拍有唔同的表現手法<br />\n一張有故事性的照片可以令人目不轉睛<br />\n而你的作品背後的故事性有待加強<br />\n#11 建議轉黑白<br />\n架藍色貨車略嫌搶左少許focus<br />\n你好多街拍都有個明顯主角<br />\n然後搭個背景<br />\n但係要試下留意下現場有無其它的人和物<br />\n可以同主角有個關聯，甚或一個對比<br />\n如果呢位老人坐係度一般時間<br />\n你都不妨係隔離扮講電話<br />\n等一個 candid moment<br />\n<br />\n#20<br />\n最鍾意呢張<br />\n唯一想講係:有無諗過轉黑白?<br />\n<br />\n#44<br />\n光影明暗係一個較直接的手法呈現主體<br />\n多嘗試係早上或黃昏出動<br />\n呢張相入面陽光打落老伯塊面<br />\n令人睇到佢面貌輪廓<br />\n呢樣都係街拍其中一種重要元素<br />\n香港人出街好多時都木口木面<br />\n所以影的時候要有觸覺"},{"pid":"17dc42a9bfadb2dc826e722eea3c6b75cb70a454","tid":516314,"uid":65495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babc5db671d087ce96e3358ce3c82f6c918b137e","tid":516314,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"好似12，18，25嗰啲我都好鐘意<br />\n<br />\n但係放係攝台都會被人留低負皮同膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"Sad but...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb30de1af69cbb1d8281f54d6d62b6e069b78ad","tid":516314,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"956bfead242eaeea2f2f727bdb6b42a5e3e77810","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宜家多左出去行，不過快門明顯㩒少左，覺得好多畫面都唔夠好咁<br />\n由以前一半出去一個下午一定影到一筒，到宜家基本上可能得半筒<br />\n唔知咁樣係唔係一件好事，不過滿意嘅作品相對多左<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凈係呢幾句野，其實我都唔知邊樣先啱。<br />\n<br />\n同你剛好倒轉，之前勁慳快門用勁多時間構圖諗清楚先㩒，錯失左好多機會，風景的話又真係輛率高好多，不過ｓｎａｐ　成日覺得背景亂構圖唔靚就唔影，ｍｉｓｓ　好多野喇<br />\n<br />\n而家風景ｓｎａｐｓｈｏｔ要兩個ｍｏｄｅ都仲適應緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"其實影咩題材都唔洗就住就住啦, 又唔係影菲林, 即使係所謂靜態風景相, 淨係有風吹郁左個d 樹葉, 水面嘅波紋 或者穿透雲層嘅光線都已經令張相唔同左, 個人覺得要進步唯一要做嘅就係影多d"},{"pid":"215ee178536b8b0951ab7c1bea5a25efa35c9957","tid":516314,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eb30de1af69cbb1d8281f54d6d62b6e069b78ad","tid":516314,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"956bfead242eaeea2f2f727bdb6b42a5e3e77810","tid":516314,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宜家多左出去行，不過快門明顯㩒少左，覺得好多畫面都唔夠好咁<br />\n由以前一半出去一個下午一定影到一筒，到宜家基本上可能得半筒<br />\n唔知咁樣係唔係一件好事，不過滿意嘅作品相對多左<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凈係呢幾句野，其實我都唔知邊樣先啱。<br />\n<br />\n同你剛好倒轉，之前勁慳快門用勁多時間構圖諗清楚先㩒，錯失左好多機會，風景的話又真係輛率高好多，不過ｓｎａｐ　成日覺得背景亂構圖唔靚就唔影，ｍｉｓｓ　好多野喇<br />\n<br />\n而家風景ｓｎａｐｓｈｏｔ要兩個ｍｏｄｅ都仲適應緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"其實影咩題材都唔洗就住就住啦, 又唔係影菲林, 即使係所謂靜態風景相, 淨係有風吹郁左個d 樹葉, 水面嘅波紋 或者穿透雲層嘅光線都已經令張相唔同左, 個人覺得要進步唯一要做嘅就係影多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:06:58.000Z","msg":"樓主好似講過係影菲林喎<br />\n<br />\n不過影多d係需要<br />\n同埋影多d， specific 黎講<br />\n係要同一個環境試下唔同角度、構圖、環境氣氛等等<br />\n到最後再揀一張心水出黎"},{"pid":"6a498ae4330f3fc846c5924b71ace553d8080684","tid":516314,"uid":14919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17dc42a9bfadb2dc826e722eea3c6b75cb70a454","tid":516314,"uid":65495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babc5db671d087ce96e3358ce3c82f6c918b137e","tid":516314,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"好似12，18，25嗰啲我都好鐘意<br />\n<br />\n但係放係攝台都會被人留低負皮同膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-